Usage: bitblast_ports [-help] <topCell|vCell|hInst>+ [-bus <name>]

-help                      # Prints out the command usage
<topCell|vCell|hInst>+     # List of design/module/hinst
                           # ((topCell|vCell|hInst)+, required)
-bus <name>                # Name of bus port/hport (string, optional)